dct_title_s: A new map of North America : wherein is exactly described all ye European settlements, with whatever else is remarkable in the West Indies, from the latest and best discoveries; adorn'd with views and plans of the most considerable towns, harbours, &c
dct_description_sm: Various insets of cities, harbors and pictorial views.
